data.description: Welcome to your like-new dream townhome living experience! This pristine 3-bedroom, 2-full bath, 1/2 bath end-corner unit is a shining gem, meticulously crafted in 2019 and boasting 1,967 square feet of luxurious modern living space.    Step inside to discover an inviting open-concept layout where style meets functionality in perfect harmony. Natural light cascades through the expansive windows, illuminating the elegant interior and creating a warm, welcoming atmosphere throughout the day. Gather around the cozy electric fireplace in the family room, creating an inviting ambiance that's perfect for relaxation and intimate gatherings.    The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek white cabinets, pristine granite countertops, and state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances that effortlessly blend style and practicality. Upgraded LVP flooring on the main level adds durability and charm, while plush newer gray carpeting leads you to the upper level, where three generously sized bedrooms await.    Indulge in the luxurious primary bathroom sanctuary, adorned with exquisite tile work around the tub and shower shelves. Pamper yourself in the separate tub and shower, complete with a double vanity for added convenience. The master bedroom boasts tray ceilings, a large closet, and more, providing the perfect retreat after a long day.  For your peace of mind, this home comes equipped with an alarm system offering remote accessibility and a privacy vinyl fence. Plus, enjoy the convenience of total electric and energy-efficient living, with HOA maintenance covering exterior upkeep, lawn care, siding, and roof maintenance for just $110 monthly.    Benefit from the current owner's upkeep, which includes biannual HVAC service and quarterly pest control, ensuring comfort and cleanliness year-round. With the added bonus of an assumable FHA loan at a 5.25% interest rate, this is truly an opportunity not to be missed. Welcome home to luxury, comfort, and convenience. Schedule your viewing today!
